      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
                 throws java.lang.Exception
        Java main() interface to interact with ExcelToFoConverter

        Usage: ExcelToHtmlConverter infile outfile

        Where infile is an input .xls file ( Word 97-2007) which will be rendered as XSL FO into outfile        (与ExcelToFoEditor交互的Java main（）接口使用：ExcelToPtmlEditor infile outfile其中infile是输入.xls文件（Word 97-2007），将作为NSX FO呈现到outfile中)
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception(java.lang.Exception)
